

### Registrar admin
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/registrar
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nome": "Admin",
  "email": "admin@locadora.com",
  "senha": "1234",
  "role": "admin"
}

### Registrar funcionario
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/registrar
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nome": "Funcionario 1",
  "email": "func1@locadora.com",
  "senha": "1234",
  "role": "funcionario"
}










